<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/AssertionCredential> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/AssertionCredential> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Assertion Credential"@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/AssertionCredential> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "\n  A Verifiable Credential that expresses a factual statement about an identifiable subject as a subject, predicate, and object.\n\n  Assertion credentials use predicates to represent domain-specific facts, such as licences, compliance statuses, capabilities, or authorities, without introducing specialised credential schemas for each fact type.\n  "@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/object> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/object> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "object"@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/object> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "\n  The value of the asserted fact. The object can be expressed as a URI, a literal value, or a structured JSON-LD value.\n  "@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/object> <http://schema.org/domainIncludes> <https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/AssertionCredential> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/predicate> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/predicate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "predicate"@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/predicate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "\n  The property or relationship being asserted about the subject.\n  "@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/predicate> <http://schema.org/domainIncludes> <https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/AssertionCredential> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/predicate> <http://schema.org/rangeIncludes> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/scope> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/scope> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "scope"@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/scope> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "\n  The context, zone, policy, or other resource within which the assertion applies.\n  "@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/scope> <http://schema.org/domainIncludes> <https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/AssertionCredential> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/scope> <http://schema.org/rangeIncludes> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/subject> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/subject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "subject"@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/subject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "\n  The identifiable subject the fact is asserted about.\n  "@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/subject> <http://schema.org/domainIncludes> <https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/AssertionCredential> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/subject> <http://schema.org/rangeIncludes> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/supportingEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#Property> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/supportingEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "supporting evidence"@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/supportingEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "\n  A resource that supports or documents the asserted fact.\n  "@en .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/supportingEvidence> <http://schema.org/domainIncludes> <https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/AssertionCredential> .
<https://w3id.org/axone/ontology/v5/schema/core/assertion/supportingEvidence> <http://schema.org/rangeIncludes> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
